title: Outsource Web Apps to Afghanistan
text:
I've worked as a developer for two distinct firms in New Zealand, and both of them outsourced their product development to the Philippines before we maintained it here.

I wish to assist the citizens of Afghanistan, where I am from. Therefore, if you run a firm and are working on a software project (Web). Let's connect, please.

Tell HN: HN needs to tweak the gravity of “Ask HN:” posts
text: Maybe it's just me (I guess so b/c "Ask HNs" are very popular) but I find their topics often to be kind of irrelevant, too meta, full of random rambling and having a tonality of a Reddit AMA. Not always but yeah. It's no dealbreaker and I can just hide them but seeing them in the feed sends some aftertaste letting me leave HN quickly again.
